### NexusCanon AXIS API Testing
### Use this file with REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Echo API
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/echo
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "message": "Hello from REST Client"
}

### Get All Requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/requests
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Get Request by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/requests/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Approve Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/requests/1/approve
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "approvedBy": "user@example.com"
}

### Get Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Auth - Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Auth - Signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "New User"
}

### Auth - Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
